- MaterialRef is a transparent alias of RenderMaterialRef (references.ts:70). RenderMaterialRef carries id, mediaKind, locator, producerExtensionId, producerVersion, provenance, determinism, replacementPolicy (artifacts.ts:172-181). This satisfies the identity contract for material references in transition slots.
